Package: interactionHR
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Hazard Ratios in Cox Models with Interaction
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2021-10-28
Author: Giorgio Melloni, Andrea Bellavia
Maintainer: Giorgio Melloni <melloni.giorgio@gmail.com>
Description: A tool to calculate and plot Hazard Ratios on a Cox model in which an interaction between the main predictor and a continuous covariate has been specified.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6)
